{"tid":1506932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔請幫手- 通緝","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:28:39.000Z","uid":206272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e6584b44acc7b491a05aa5036fb31074ec18a22","tid":1506932,"uid":206272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"尋日下午大約5-6點，係荃灣大鴻輝十字路口。<br />\n有手足係到set 緊路障，放緊沙包係馬路。<br />\n有架白色Volkswagen Golf 突然衝過去手足到，<br />\n剷過沙包走。架車去到下個燈位紅燈停左，<br />\n有幾個手足衝上去燈位，但之後佢衝燈追唔到佢。<br />\n<br />\n有無手足記得咩車牌 / 有片 / 相？ <br />\n好似號碼係3383 尾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uUxhxGT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuUxhxGT.jpg&h=69873b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avG2JOy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavG2JOy.png&h=2cb10c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無連仔幫到手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aadc9382345f63bc35e0aa4fece8725741fbe85e","tid":1506932,"uid":206272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"自己推下先~推到有人睇到"},{"pid":"1bfc6873c3b3e50e0f7d407e280f3c86d8373e90","tid":1506932,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=d3df130e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a95e4de5eac1fbfe8bb277ca8cf726ece4775662","tid":1506932,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"推，但建議開過個新post<br />\n標題寫返日子時間地點&amp;通緝咩車撞向人群"}]}